It all begins with a dream.

Six months ago, I reached out to @kiimbedoya and @ayoarod , sharing my vision with them. I expressed my desire to establish my hospitality group “Sketchie Entertainment Group” for it to host exclusive dinner occasions for celebrities and athletes in New York City, eventually expanding throughout the United States. With 15 years of honing my skills, I have dedicated myself to ensuring that we surpass all expectations, be it for regular events or special occasions.

My entire team “Sketchie Entertainment Group” understands the power of dinner events in bringing people together. Today, I had the incredible opportunity to organize an exceptional dinner to celebrate the release of a new single by Puerto Rican artist @deivpr .The venue of choice was the @eatstk and it was truly a remarkable experience. I am immensely grateful to the entire team at Underwater Music Group for granting me the chance to exceed expectations. 

📸: @flowgenius
📍: @sketchieentgroup

I derive immense joy from organizing this Friday event with my team. We have eagerly awaited its realization for two years, and now it is finally here—the “Rooftop Garden Fridays at @maracanyc.”

Every Friday, we gather people from diverse cultures and musical genres to experience a night filled with live entertainment. It is our relentless dedication that drives us to tirelessly work, ensuring that we offer the most exceptional Friday party imaginable.

“Sketchie Entertainment Group,” @sketchieentgroup we embody the spirit of downtown uptown, and customer service is always our foremost priority.
